==趣事==
英國的《[[每日郵報|每日郵報]]》指出，丽贝卡十分爱[[鞋|鞋]]，有收集鞋子的喜好，她的鞋櫃據稱有30多雙鞋。而在入選英國泳隊後，她的母親購買一雙「克里斯提·鲁布托」（Christian Louboutin）金色高跟鞋送她作為獎勵，價值275[[英鎊|英鎊]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://2008.cns.com.cn/news/2008/08-13/28719.shtml |title=中新奧運網：英国新科泳后阿德林顿是个鞋痴 鞋柜有30多双鞋 |access-date=2008-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304130237/http://2008.cns.com.cn/news/2008/08-13/28719.shtml |archive-date=2016-03-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/femail/article-1043557/Golden-girl-Rebecca-Adlington-inspired-Olympic-swim-triumph-Jimmy-Choo-promise.html |title=Golden girl Rebecca Adlington inspired to Olympic swim triumph by Jimmy Choo promise |accessdate=2008-08-27 |archive-date=2020-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200512045438/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/femail/article-1043557/Golden-girl-Rebecca-Adlington-inspired-Olympic-swim-triumph-Jimmy-Choo-promise.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。凱旋返國後，丽贝卡再獲家鄉市長送贈一對價值460英鎊的「周仰傑」（Jimmy Choo）鞋子。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-1049433/15-000-fans-turn-greet-Britains-golden-girl-Rebecca-pair-Jimmy-Choos.html |title=15,000 fans turn out to greet Britain's golden girl Rebecca with a pair of Jimmy Choos |accessdate=2008-08-27 |archive-date=2020-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200512045443/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-1049433/15-000-fans-turn-greet-Britains-golden-girl-Rebecca-pair-Jimmy-Choos.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

